- "Leading the pack" means ranking first;
- "Average points per game" is calculated by dividing the total points scored by the total number of games played.

sql:
SELECT player_name
FROM players
WHERE contract_end_date = (
  SELECT MAX(contract_end_date)
  FROM players
);

external_knowledge:
- "Mountain range" represents the collection of teams;
- "Height of the mountain" represents the tallest player in each team;
- "Peak of the mountain range" represents the tallest player across all teams.

sql:
SELECT MAX(max_height) AS tallest_player_height
FROM (
  SELECT MAX(height) AS max_height
  FROM players
  GROUP BY team_id
);

